                    default_next: None,
                ),
                (
                    speaker: "Admiral",
                    line: "A Mockingbird. Big as a galleon's mainsail, mean as low water. Snatched the iron-bound chest right off the bar. Left us a feather, two splinters, and an apology in a voice that wasn't its own.",
                    options: [
